<!--
  :overlay-yggdrasil library manifest. Empty for now (Phase α — scaffold
  only, no daemon shipped). When the yggdrasil binary lands the manifest
  will declare a foreground VpnService since Yggdrasil's transport is a
  full IPv6 mesh — exposed as a tun, not a SOCKS port. That's a different
  shape from i2pd / lokinet (both of which ship as userspace SOCKS) but
  the status pub/sub contract here is identical so consumer UI doesn't
  have to special-case.
-->
